transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan ji sir, haan ji sir aa gaye aap system pe hai na?
Executive: Ji sir.
Customer: Ji toh ek kaam hai na aapko bhej raha hu sir.

Executive: Join karega sir.
Ki sir mobile pe join karenge ya phir laptop desktop pe sir?
Customer: Sir is time pe mai toh is time mai phone pe hi join karunga.
Executive: Achha phone pe hi karenge na?
Customer: Ji sir.
Executive: Okay toh phone se kar lijiye.

Executive: Dekhiye sir ek mail mil gaya aapko?
Customer: Ji sir.
Executive: Join kar lijiye sir.

Executive: Mail mila sir maine kiya hoga aapko mail video link.
Customer: Mujhe toh WhatsApp kar do.
Executive: Nahi nahi sir.

Executive: Ji aap ho gaye join.
[unintelligible]
Executive: Aap jis vyakti se baat kar rahe hai unhone aapke call ko hold pe
